      <title>德桑蒂斯为担心反犹太主义的犹太人转学到佛罗里达大学提供激励</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/desantis-offers-incentives-for-jewish-students-worried-about-antisemitism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[佛罗里达州州长罗恩·德桑蒂斯为担心反犹太主义的犹太学生就读该州的大学提供了激励措施，延续了他长期支持以色列的美国总统竞选的关键主题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/desantis-offers-incentives-for-jewish-students-worried-about-antisemitism</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 01:13:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马里兰州州长表示，特朗普再次担任总统将导致枪支管制倒退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/donald-trump-win-to-lead-to-gun-control-rollback-maryland-governor-wes-moore</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主党马里兰州州长韦斯·摩尔表示，唐纳德·特朗普在 11 月的胜利将带来枪支管制的“重大倒退”，他向党内基础选民发出关于这位共和党领跑者重返白宫的影响的警告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/donald-trump-win-to-lead-to-gun-control-rollback-maryland-governor-wes-moore</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 00:55:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金正恩称韩国为“主要敌人”，引发热议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/kim-jong-un-calls-south-korea-principal-enemy-turning-up-heat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜领导人金正恩加大了对韩国的施压力度，称其为“主要敌人”，显然是为了影响邻国即将举行的选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/kim-jong-un-calls-south-korea-principal-enemy-turning-up-heat</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 00:21:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刚果宪法法院确认菲利克斯·齐塞克迪赢得选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/congo-s-constitutional-court-confirms-felix-tshisekedi-s-election-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[刚果民主共和国宪法法院确认总统费利克斯·齐塞克迪在该国 12 月 20 日的选举中取得压倒性胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/congo-s-constitutional-court-confirms-felix-tshisekedi-s-election-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 00:02:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美中恢复当面军事政策协调会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/us-china-resume-in-person-military-policy-coordination-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国和中国国防官员周一和周二在五角大楼举行了政策协调会谈——这是自冠状病毒大流行之前以来的首次此类面对面会议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/us-china-resume-in-person-military-policy-coordination-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 23:12:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平提升中国与创纪录国家的关系以对抗美国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/xi-elevates-ties-with-record-number-of-nations-to-counter-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平去年与创纪录数量的国家升级了外交关系，寻求团结全球南方，帮助重塑美国领导的世界秩序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/xi-elevates-ties-with-record-number-of-nations-to-counter-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>为了保护选举不受中国影响，台湾剥夺了数千选民的选举权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/protecting-taiwan-s-election-from-china-has-meant-disenfranchises-thousands</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保护台湾的选举免受中国潜在的干扰是自治民主国家非常关心的问题，以至于多年来它一直愿意为此剥夺数十万合格选民的选举权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/protecting-taiwan-s-election-from-china-has-meant-disenfranchises-thousands</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议院共和党人在政府关门截止日期前提议更新短期资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/senate-gop-floats-renewing-short-term-funding-as-shutdown-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院共和党领导人周二在评论中表示，国会将需要另一项临时支出措施，以避免 1 月 20 日部分政府关门，这可能会引发众议院保守派的强烈反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/senate-gop-floats-renewing-short-term-funding-as-shutdown-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 20:39:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡移植机构完成涉及交通部长的调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/singapore-completes-probe-related-to-transport-minister-paper</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡已经完成了对其一名最高级别部长的腐败案件的长达数月的调查，该调查在去年震惊了这个以廉洁治理而闻名的城市国家的调查中取得了进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/singapore-completes-probe-related-to-transport-minister-paper</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 11:50:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾卫星空袭警报引发选前焦虑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/taiwan-activates-air-raid-alert-after-chinese-satellite-fly-over</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾针对中国卫星发射发出空袭警报，这一事件在关键的总统选举前几天引起了一些焦虑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/taiwan-activates-air-raid-alert-after-chinese-satellite-fly-over</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 08:02:44 GMT</pubDate>
